text: Sergei Karimov (German:Sergej Karimow, Russian: Сергей Каримов) (21 December 1986 – 24 December 2019)"Er wurde nur 33 Jahre alt: Der VfL Wolfsburg trauert um Ex-Profi Sergej Karimow " sportbuzzer.de 26 December 2019 was a Kazakh footballer. He last played for Lupo Martini Wolfsburg. In 2010, he played for the Kazakhstan national football team. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Kazakhstani sportspeople Category:European footballers
title: Sergei Karimov
